N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7903.1 - Purpose and scope

State Regulations

This part establishes procedures for issuance of State
set-aside assignment orders and denial orders issued pursuant to Part 7901 of
this subchapter, and State set-aside general distribution orders issued
pursuant to Part 7902 of this subchapter. Notes

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
